         <p class="breadcrumbs">You are here: <a href="/en.html?id=4">Government.no</a> / <a href="/en/dep/kd.html?id=586">Ministry of Education and R...</a> / <a href="/en/dep/kd/Selected-topics.html?id=588">Selected Topics</a> / <span>International Collaboration on Education and Research</span>
